        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Gong Woo-Jin (Yang Se-Jong) is a 30-year-old single man and he works as a set designer. Due to a trauma he experienced 13 years ago, he does not want to have a relationship with others.\n\nWhen Woo Seo-Ri (Shin Hae-Sun) was 17, she fell into a coma. 13 years later, she wakes up from her coma. Her mental age is still that of a 17-year-old, but she is now 30-years-old.\n\nGong Woo-Jin and Woo Seo-Ri get involved with each other and fall in love.",
